text: LA-15 is a constituency of Azad Kashmir Legislative Assembly which is currently represented by Sardar Mir Akbar Khan of Pakistan Muslim League (N). It covers the area of Eastern Bagh Tehsil in Bagh District of Azad Kashmir, Pakistan. ==Election 2016== elections were held in this constituency on 21 July 2016.
